                <td bgcolor="#37437B" valign="top"><font color="white" face="verdana" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;01/23/2004&nbsp;: 12:46:05 PM</small><hr size="1"><span class="spnMessageText"> Oh, and it'll give you time to practice 'med kiting'.  If you don't already know what that is, it's sitting, waiting for a tick of mana, then immediately standing and moving away from the mob for about 4 seconds, then sitting again just before the next tick of mana hits, then standing again and repeating until the mob is dead...let's you move and med at the same time.<br /><br />Animocity S'eething<br />Arch Lich<br />Stromm</span></font></td>
